.TH xsetpointer 1 __vendorversion__
.SH NAME
xsetpointer \- set an X Input device as the main pointer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xsetpointer \-l
|
.I device-name
.SH DESCRIPTION
Xsetpointer sets an XInput device as the main pointer.  When called with
the \-l flag it lists the available devices.
